text:
@SebJohnsonUK @fractile_ai Check out $IQE. 
Has already benefitted from this Semis run after a massive decline from all time highs. 

But still poised for more upside given their photonics tech and GaN capabilities.

@babyfolio The Photonics name was $AAOI 😂😂

"This morning, April 10, Andrew Left of Citron Research posted his short position on AAOI to X.
The stock is “delusional,” the recent rally is overheated, and the whole thing was built on the back of a “random press release.”"

